OL,3,CRapist who attacked 'intoxicated,
OL,4,Cvulnerable' women jailed
OL,6,FA rapist who targeted lone woman in
OL,7,FLeeds has been jailed.
OL,9,FRashid Boachie, 44, was caught after
OL,10,FCCTV footage showed him approaching a
OL,11,Fwoman who was on a night out.
OL,13,FHe led her to an alleyway behind a
OL,14,FTravelodge and exually assaulted her
OL,15,Fbut fled when a hotel staff member
OL,16,Fheard her shouting and intervened.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/5
