OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1774624292
OL,3,CRapist who attacked 'intoxicated,
OL,4,Cvulnerable' women jailed
OL,6,FBoachie was arrested four days after
OL,7,Fthe incident in August last year and
OL,8,FDNA samples taken while he was in
OL,9,Fcustody linked him to the rape of a
OL,10,Fwoman in Beeston four years earlier.
OL,12,FIn that incident a woman got into his
OL,13,Fcar believing it was a taxi. He drove
OL,14,Fher to two car parks before stopping
OL,15,Fat an empty one where he raped her.
OL,17,FDuring the incident, she recorded a
OL,18,Fshort video message in which she could
OL,19,Fbe heard saying "help me".
OL,26,@{D@QOU{D@YO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/5
