PN,36803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1774624292
OL,3,CRapist who attacked 'intoxicated,
OL,4,Cvulnerable' women jailed
OL,6,FBoachie was convicted of rape and
OL,7,Fsexual assault and was given an
OL,8,Fextended sentence with a prison term
OL,9,Fof 15-and-a-half years.
OL,11,FDet Insp Jodie Hayes, of West
OL,12,FYorkshire Police, said Boachie may
OL,13,Fhave committed other offences which
OL,14,Fhad not come to light.
OL,16,FShe said: "He is a dangerous sexual
OL,17,Fpredator who has deliberately preyed
OL,18,Fon heavily intoxicated, vulnerable
OL,19,Fwomen who have become separated from
OL,20,Ftheir friends and will hopefully now
OL,21,Fbe behind bars for a long time."
OL,26,@xD@KOU}D@`O]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/5
