FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1774624292
OL,3,CRapist who attacked 'intoxicated,
OL,4,Cvulnerable' women jailed
OL,6,F"Members of the public played a
OL,7,Fvaluable role in helping us identify
OL,8,FBoachie in the CCTV images from the
OL,9,F2025 offence. By arresting him for
OL,10,Fthat offence, we were able to then
OL,11,Flink him back to the earlier offence.
OL,13,F"There were four years between these
OL,14,Foffences and there is potential that
OL,15,FBoachie has committed other crimes
OL,16,Fduring that time. If anyone has been a
OL,17,Fvictim of an offence, we would urge
OL,18,Fthem to report it."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUzD@SO]
